{"tid":1911994,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"歐洲大爆發 荷蘭，瑞典部升","createTime":"2020-03-05T17:48:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-05T18:29:54.000Z","uid":249945,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8de69e523b441592cadc68fba6d86cc0e50898e4","tid":1911994,"uid":249945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T17:48:02.000Z","msg":"mo la mo la<br />\n<br />\n香港比世界反超<br />\n連山區肺都叻過我哋<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/03/06/014629_7d51f23c88ea5af3a96bd6869838dff1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F03%2F06%2F014629_7d51f23c88ea5af3a96bd6869838dff1.png&h=66438a0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.worldometers.info/coronavirus/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.worldometers.info%2Fcoronavirus%2F&d=%2BwrRK7ySmiC6A5TqlPyaq%2FUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=5c16dcee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.worldometers.info/coronavirus/</a>"},{"pid":"d06cbb904725d6a045346530db4906d88063895c","tid":1911994,"uid":249945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T17:49:00.000Z","msg":"Belgium 都倍升"},{"pid":"5becfc9145972d3f28f3915ee7bc1789f9f67fa1","tid":1911994,"uid":233228,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T17:53:10.000Z","msg":"因為唔戴口罩先增得咁快"},{"pid":"047b85d8a7543815c722e30f2638b82d5de63bbb","tid":1911994,"uid":304769,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T17:56:29.000Z","msg":"大家日日戴口罩真係好正確<br />\n<br />\n想消滅支那，我們就要帶領支畜暴動和革命，才有機會從內部瓦解支共（輸出革命+加速主義，缺一不可）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1911527\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1911527</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n唔想香港淪為支那賤畜之境，大家必須肅清中資，整頓&ldquo;港漂&rdquo;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1902243\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1902243</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n（國際戰線）借助日韓爆發武肺推動全球反奶共運動和全球排支運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1894747\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1894747</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n中資禍港數十年，若不肅清，真香港人恐將不復存在<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1810669\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1810669</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n必須先紅後藍，否則中共恐成最後贏家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1809175\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1809175</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"88a851db2299f90dd0abd2a71dc71883989d43cd","tid":1911994,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T18:21:39.000Z","msg":"意粉有潛力爬泡菜頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"097d93edad9f7ac183af53d9ebb5d42e6c0c4873","tid":1911994,"uid":18912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T18:25:19.000Z","msg":"瘋了瘋了都瘋了"},{"pid":"7145e9b787a4f5710023246d943202dd01183e80","tid":1911994,"uid":41768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T18:29:54.000Z","msg":"伊朗個上升好似直升機咁 <br />\n上星期先話幾廿單<br />\n以家3千幾"}]}